<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="讀誦" xml:id="gsz0864c04shiChuJin"><lb
ed="T" n="0864c04"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0864c04"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000042321"><placeName>京師</placeName><placeName>千福寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A009174">楚金</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0864c05"/><persName key="A009174">釋楚金</persName>，<name>程</name>氏之子，本<placeName key="PL000000001748">廣平郡</placeName>，今為<placeName key="PL000000042192">京兆</placeName>之<placeName key="PL000000042598">盩<lb
ed="T" n="0864c06"/>厔</placeName>人也<ptr target="#n3013"/>。母<persName key="A019468">高<roleName>氏</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n3014"/>夜夢諸佛，因而妊焉，生實<lb
ed="T" n="0864c07"/><persName key="A002799">法王</persName>之子也。行素顏玉，神和氣清。<date key="j19782341978588" from-iso="+0704-02-14" to-iso="+0705-02-02">七歲</date>諷《法<lb
ed="T" n="0864c08"/>華》<ptr target="#n3015"/>，<date key="j19822511982604" from-iso="+0715-02-13" to-iso="+0716-02-01">十八</date>通其義<ptr target="#n3016"/>。<date key="j19866211987004" from-iso="+0727-01-31" to-iso="+0728-02-18">三十</date>，構塔曰<placeName key="PL000000057377">多寶</placeName><ptr target="#n677"/>。<date key="j19902441990608" from-iso="+0737-01-01" to-iso="+0737-12-31">四十</date>，入<lb
ed="T" n="0864c09"/>帝夢於九重<ptr target="#n682"/>，<persName key="A000291">玄宗</persName>覩法名下見<persName key="A009174">金</persName>字，詰朝<lb
ed="T" n="0864c10"/>使問，罔不有孚。于時聲騰<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京輦</ref>，遂<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>慕</sic><corr>募</corr></choice>人<lb
ed="T" n="0864c11"/>構塔，累級而成，有同反掌。甞於<placeName key="PL000000042513">翠微</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000042558">悟<lb
ed="T" n="0864c12"/>真</placeName>，捫蘿<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1996"/>靈趾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1997"/>，乃曰：「此<ref type="person" target="#A009174">吾</ref>棲遁之所。」遂奏<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042513 #PL000000042558">兩<lb
ed="T" n="0864c13"/>寺</ref>各建一塔，咸以「多寶」為名。此外吟詠《妙<lb
ed="T" n="0864c14"/>經》<ptr target="#n2996"/>六千餘遍。寶樹之下，髣髴見於分身；<placeName key="PL000000048268">靈山</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0864c15"/>之中，依俙覿<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1442"/>於三變<ptr target="#n3017"/>。心無所得，舌流甘露；<lb
ed="T" n="0864c16"/>瑞鳥金碧，棲於手中；天樂清泠，奏于空際。凡<lb
ed="T" n="0864c17"/>諸休應<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1998"/>，皆不有之。乃曰：「法象王之法駕<ptr target="#n683"/>，迴<lb
ed="T" n="0864c18"/>人主之宸睠，承明<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1999"/>三入，揚法六宮，后妃長跪<lb
ed="T" n="0864c19"/>於御筵，天<anchor xml:id="beg0864sgsz14"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0864sgsz14"/>分散而不著。<persName key="A000291">明皇</persName>題額，<persName key="A004378">肅宗</persName>賜<lb
ed="T" n="0864c20"/><anchor xml:id="beg0864002"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>旛</sic><corr>幡</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0864002"/>，……豈榮冠於一時？亦庶幾於佛在也！」以<lb
ed="T" n="0864c21"/><date key="j19984981998498" when-iso="+0759-08-08"><name>乾元</name>二年七月七日</date>子時，右脇示滅焉。薪盡<ptr type="glossary" target="#g152"/><lb
ed="T" n="0864c22"/>火滅，雪顏如在，昭乎上生於安養之國<ptr type="glossary" target="#g843"/>矣。<lb
ed="T" n="0864c23"/>春秋六十二，法臘三十七。<ref type="person" target="#A004378">天子</ref>憫焉，中使<anchor xml:id="beg0864sgsz16"/>弔<anchor xml:id="end0864sgsz16"/><lb
ed="T" n="0864c24"/>焉。勅驃騎大將軍<persName key="A010268">朱光暉</persName>監護，即以其法<lb
ed="T" n="0864c25"/>葬于城西<placeName key="PL000000042173"><placeName>龍首原</placeName><placeName>法華蘭若</placeName></placeName>，塔之<ptr target="#n3018"/>。初<persName key="A009174">金</persName>髫年<lb
ed="T" n="0864c26"/>寫《法華經》，不衣縑繒，寒加艾納<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1322"/>而已。弟子<lb
ed="T" n="0864c27"/><persName key="A010329">慧空</persName>、<persName key="A013555">法岸</persName>、<persName key="A013556">浩然</persName>皆隨象王之子也。<placeName key="PL000000042657"><placeName>紫閣峯</placeName><placeName>草<lb
ed="T" n="0864c28"/>堂寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A000888">飛錫</persName>碑文，<persName key="A011107">吳通微</persName>書。至<date key="j20122952012295" when-iso="+0797-05-17"><name>貞元</name>十三年四<lb
ed="T" n="0864c29"/>月十三日</date>左街功德使開府<persName key="A009162"><persName>邠國公</persName><persName>竇文場</persName></persName><pb ed="T" n="0865a" xml:id="T50.2061.0865a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0865a01"/>奏「<placeName key="PL000000042321">千福寺</placeName>先師<persName key="A009174">楚金</persName>是臣和尚<ptr target="#n3020"/>，於<date key="j19921141993438" notAfter-iso="+0745-09-30" notBefore-iso="+0742-02-14"><name>天寶</name><lb
ed="T" n="0865a02"/>初</date>為國建<placeName key="PL000000057377">多寶塔</placeName>，置法華道場，經今六十<lb
ed="T" n="0865a03"/>餘祀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1230"/>。僧等六時<anchor xml:id="beg0865sgsz1"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0865sgsz1"/>念，經聲不斷，以歷四朝，<lb
ed="T" n="0865a04"/>未蒙旌德。……<ptr target="#n3019"/>」勅謚<persName key="A009174">大圓禪師</persName>矣！<ptr target="#n3021"/></p>
